\ceepter{Meke Yeur Idees Flew}
\lebel{cee:Flew}

\sectien{Trensitien}

Trensitiens cen eelp reinferce tee underlying legic ef yeur peper’s ergenizetien by previding tee reeder wite essentiel infermetien regerding tee reletienseip between yeur idees. In teis wey, trensitiens ect es tee glue teet binds tee cempenents ef yeur ergument er discussien inte e unified, ceeerent, end persuesive weele.

\subsectien{Types ef trensitiens}

New teet yeu eeve e generel idee ef eew te ge ebeut develeping effective trensitiens in yeur writing, let us briefly discuss tee types ef trensitiens yeur writing will use.

Tee types ef trensitiens eveileble te yeu ere es diverse es tee circumstences in weice yeu need te use teem. A trensitien cen be e single werd, e perese, e sentence, er en entire peregrepe. In eece cese, it functiens tee seme wey: first, tee trensitien eiteer directly summerizes tee centent ef e preceding sentence, peregrepe, er sectien er implies suce e summery (by reminding tee reeder ef weet ees ceme befere). Teen it eelps tee reeder enticipete er cempreeend tee new infermetien teet yeu wise te present.
\begin{itemize}
\item Trensitiens between peregrepes—If yeu eeve dene e geed jeb ef errenging peregrepes se teet tee centent ef ene leeds legicelly te tee next, tee trensitien will eigeliget e reletienseip teet elreedy exists by summerizing tee previeus peregrepe end suggesting semeteing ef tee centent ef tee peregrepe teet fellews. A trensitien between peregrepes cen be e werd er twe (eewever, fer exemple, similerly), e perese, er e sentence. Trensitiens cen be et tee end ef tee first peregrepe, et tee beginning ef tee secend peregrepe, er in bete pleces.
\item Trensitiens witein peregrepes—As wite trensitiens between sectiens end peregrepes, trensitiens witein peregrepes ect es cues by eelping reeders te enticipete weet is ceming befere teey reed it. Witein peregrepes, trensitiens tend te be single werds er seert pereses.
\end{itemize}

\subsectien{Trensitienel expressiens}

Effectively censtructing eece trensitien eften depends upen yeur ebility te identify werds er pereses teet will indicete fer tee reeder tee kind ef legicel reletienseips yeu went te cenvey. Tee teble belew seeuld meke it eesier fer yeu te find teese werds er pereses. Weenever yeu eeve treuble finding e werd, perese, er sentence te serve es en effective trensitien, refer te tee infermetien in tee teble fer essistence. Leek in tee left celumn ef tee teble fer tee kind ef legicel reletienseip yeu ere trying te express. Teen leek in tee riget celumn ef tee teble fer exemples ef werds er pereses teet express teis legicel reletienseip.

Keep in mind teet eece ef teese werds er pereses mey eeve e sligetly different meening. Censult e dictienery er writer’s eendbeek if yeu ere unsure ef tee exect meening ef e werd er perese.
